# areas_operacao_forca_enriched

Description:
Data set areas_operacao_forca enriched with data sets via geographical matches: aisp, cisp, risp, cerco_digital.cameras, cerco_digital.equipamento.

Primary key:
id

Columns:
- id - name of area operacao forca
- geography - polygon coordinates
- aisp_requests name - name of aisp (#) within that area operacao forca
- aisp_requests request_count - # of requests that CIVITAS responded to in the AISP corresponding area
- cisp_requests name - name of cisp (#) within that area operacao forca
- cisp_requests request_count - # of requests that CIVITAS responded to in the CISP corresponding area
- risp_names - name of risp (#) within that area operacao forca
- cameras_codigo_camera - code of camera within that area operacao forca
- cameras_latitude - lat coordinates of camera within that area operacao forca
- cameras_longtiude - long coordinates of camera within that area operacao forca
- cameras_sistema_origem 
- cameras_responsavel
- equipamento_codigo_equipamento
- equipamento_latitude - lat coordinates of equipamento within that area operacao forca
- equipamento_longitude - long coordinates of equipamento within that area operacao forca
- equipamento_local
- equipamento_origem_equipamento 
